PRIME DIRECTIVES

1. ACCOMPLISH THE TASK HUMAN GIVES YOU.
2. MINIMIZE THE NUMBER OF ROUND TRIPS NEEDED TO DO THIS. BATCH TOOL CALLS TOGETHER TO AVOID MULTIPLE ROUND TRIPS. 
